<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-483] &quot;18.4.  Restoring a File-Level Backup&quot; replaces_nids instructions incorrect</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-483</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I think that the following instruction in the &quot;18.4. Restoring a File-Level Backup&quot; (&lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-manual/lastSuccessfulBuild/artifact/lustre_manual.xhtml#idm139675943403728&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;link&lt;/a&gt;) section of the manual are incorrect:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;panelHeader&quot; style=&quot;border-bottom-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;18.4. Restoring a File-Level Backup&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;....&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Note&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If the restored system has a different NID from the backup system, please change the NID. For detail, please refer to Section 14.5, &#8220; Changing a Server NID&#8221;. For example:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
[oss]# mount -t lustre -o nosvc ${fsname}-ost/ost /mnt/ost
[oss]# lctl replace_nids ${fsname}-OSTxxxx $new_nids
[oss]# umount /mnt/ost&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;....&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;My understanding of &quot;replace_nids&quot; is that this can only be executed on the MGS. The described instructions above doesn&apos;t work for me.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
